@startuml State_User
title Feature 08 - User Account State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #141417
    FontColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #333333
    ArrowColor #FF5C00
}

[*] --> Anonymous

Anonymous --> Registered : Sign up\n(email or OAuth)
Anonymous --> Registered : Re-login\n(existing account)

Registered --> Onboarding : Email verified\n/ completeSignUp()

Onboarding --> Active : Complete onboarding\n(bank connected,\n first scan done)

Active --> Active : Update profile,\nchange autonomy,\nupgrade/downgrade tier

Active --> Suspended : Payment failed\n(3 consecutive)

Suspended --> Active : Payment resolved\n(webhook: invoice.paid)

Active --> Deleted : User requests deletion\n/ soft-delete, disable auth,\n cancel subscription

Suspended --> Deleted : User requests deletion

Deleted --> Active : Reactivate within\n30-day grace period

Deleted --> [*] : 30-day purge job\n/ hard-delete all data

@enduml
